//
//           PRISMA IS READ-ONLY IN THIS PROJECT
//
// SEQUELIZE REMAINS THE SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH
//
// DO NOT RUN:
// - prisma migrate dev
// - prisma migrate deploy
// - prisma db push
// - ANY write operations using PrismaClient
//
// PRISMA IS ONLY ALLOWED FOR:
// - Read operations (findMany, findUnique, findFirst)
// - Aggregation queries (count, sum, avg, groupBy)
// - Reports and analytics
//
// ALL WRITES MUST GO THROUGH SEQUELIZE:
// - create, update, upsert, delete
// - Transactions
// - Schema modifications and migrations
//
// TO UPDATE THIS SCHEMA:
// 1. Apply changes via Sequelize migrations: npm run db:migrate
// 2. Introspect the database: npx prisma@6 db pull
// 3. Regenerate client: npx prisma@6 generate
//
